metadata.description:
Hundies, a genesis collection of 900 delightful bots, inspired by the creative journey of CVillian14 and his three-year-old son's original "Hundy bot." With a focus on nurturing a community brimming with positivity, creativity, and a dash of nostalgia, Hundies is all about rediscovering the joy of shared experiences.

As the Hundies community grows and evolves, so will the adorable bots that make up this unique collection. Each Hundies holder will be part of this heartwarming journey and enjoy IP licensing opportunities, events, early access to each project in CVillian14's BIG100 experiment, and more.
metadata.name: Hundies #1
